{"type": "article", "id": 32422, "title": "光撒在山脉上，就成了一盏灯｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-20T22:58:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27564, "name": "Peleg Design"}, {"id": 32978, "name": "Tierney Haines Architects"}, {"id": 32979, "name": "Axo Light"}, {"id": 32980, "name": "Dima Loginoff"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 178, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160921064101GJ0mLwDeaAxv9BdN.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Palfrey Chair by Tierney Haines Architects</h3><p>这个名为 <a href=\"http://www.tierneyhaines.com/Palfrey-Chair\" rel=\"nofollow\">Palfrey</a> 的折叠椅是爱尔兰 <a href=\"http://tierneyhaines.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tierney Haines Architects</a> 工作室的一款概念设计，它的独特之处在于横向的折叠方式。为了做到这一点，设计师们为它打造了 X 型的铰链结构，在左右椅腿并拢的过程中，椅背会随之折叠在一起，座位则会偏向一侧与地面垂直。从解析图上可以看到，椅子的结构其实并不复杂，外形也相当简洁耐看，无论是家用还是办公都能节省不少空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003857Tj7Ct98sBvDQeng4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003857VANuUWKXSBb0wOmD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003857ZVX6Yv5ENQksmWdi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003858zopjAOwPSDKJLmxb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003857IH90sW3QekincqP1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003857FdLSXYomx9fhEwDt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>In:visible Wallet by Mosi Mosi</h3><p>对于视障群体来说，出门购物并不是件容易的事：他们需要格外仔细地通过触摸来确定纸钞面额，如果遇到了不良的商家给了错误的金额，他们很难在第一时间察觉到。为了解决这一隐忧，出身于香港理工大学设计系的梁雯蕙成立的 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Mosi-mosi-%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%8B%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E6%89%80-437013563146695/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mosi Mosi 無事無事研究所</a>为这个群体设计了这款名为 In:visible 的钱包。基于港币不同面额有不同尺寸的特点，钱包内含两块帮助人们进行对照的隔板：确认长度的隔板左下角有五条刻度线，宽度隔板则通过阶梯状的边缘进行确认。</p><p>目前这款钱包正在<a href=\"http://www.dreamna.com/lang/ch/projects/invisible-wallet/\" rel=\"nofollow\">进行集资</a>，最低金额为 100 元港币。虽然资助者自己并不会拿到钱包，但送出的钱包中会附上印有资助者姓名的盲文卡片，让收到钱包的视障人士知道是谁伸出了一臂之力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003829Qv5qp3EVmgtfx9Gu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.470000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003831aQspKrC15OB96Ncn.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613750\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003830RKjTidvDOqnGlBze.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003831q4LDtdX1nKPkQm8h.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.616250\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003830uXZ7IOmGfNwsodgV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003830uPTGbq2dyDKUCcie.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cakedozer by Peleg Design</h3><p>分完蛋糕，想要完美地把它们转移到盘子上并不是件轻松的事，家居品牌 <a href=\"https://www.peleg-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Peleg Design</a> 的设计师们就想到了这一点，在蛋糕刀手柄处设计了一个滑动槽。如此一来，只要轻轻推动推土机造型的推杆，就可以优雅地让蛋糕落在餐盘上了。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.peleg-design.com/shop/cakedozer.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 16.50 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003814FM631v7ytXgxVdzc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609210038141gf5pDvwki32SnaH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003814RJWYvoxMub2GOp9j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609210038144YBZvUKewXRgs362.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mountain View by Dima Loginoff</h3><p>把自然景观搬到家具上的设计并不少见，但大多都局限于台面，这款由俄罗斯设计师 <a href=\"http://dimaloginoff.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dima Loginoff</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.axolight.it/usa/en_GB\" rel=\"nofollow\">Axo Light</a> 设计的 <a href=\"http://www.axolight.it/usa/en_GB/products/usmounta\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mountain View</a> 吊灯或许是一个特例。线条优美的灯罩和内部精致的山脉都是由一整块玻璃吹制而成的，灯光洒在山脉上的效果会随着观察角度发生变化，带给人一种奇妙的流动感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609210036263zpRXOaeUWxAogyj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003626BVZOL4WsYlgmd37o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003626BvqHe5jR1xmWJPQ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.880469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003627SnoRtEZFCsQgkdbN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003627vs2TIUzdxr9yhW5Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003627Nc36ERLiM75mrDkz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.268333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wave by Sasha Tereshchenko</h3><p>为什么收纳柜非得是平整的？乌克兰设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/otereshc\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sasha Tereshchenko</a> 在这套名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/42593997/Concept-storage-set-Wave\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wave</a> 的概念设计中就尝试用起伏的波浪结构来挑战人们对这类物品的固有印象。上下凹凸不平的表面很适合零散地放上几本书或是钥匙一类的小物，柜子之间也可以灵活地组合出不同的造型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003609lw6FUnXGb85vVPCY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.199657\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003610YQ6P3HK85VveDnyt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.199657\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003607iSgwoUNVxG5cn4LJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003609J0eVD8H9G2OlQmz4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.599167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003612C2pZmjMX4SN7iLk3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.199657\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>First Aid Kit Redesigned by Kevin Harald Campean</h3><p>提到急救箱，你脑海中浮现的或许是一个看上去有些笨重的箱子，所有的物品都一股脑地堆砌在里面——对匈牙利设计学生 Kevin Harald Campean 来说，他的毕业设计就是对急救箱进行一次改造，让人们能够更快地找到自己需要的物品。Campean 最后借鉴了 Burgopak 的滑动结构，将急救箱分为工具类和绷带类两个上下堆叠的橙色大盒，每种物品则放置在单独的小盒中，排列得非常工整有序。小盒的包装上除了物品的基本信息外还印有 Campean 设计的一套标志，现代感十足。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003550Vl6nIHP1r7kbzB9S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003550AMPQNh9q7VCcE63F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003550FT3mD1oNewpg2OxC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702465\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003550u5JMVCHL6wK4Ygks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701413\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609210035505yuhKUOTnSDsHtAb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656140\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160921003550qJZWC98i2fFDvPRx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.350254\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}